<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Dives 8 Percent </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, August 26 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index sharply tumbled 255.99 points on Wednesday, or
7.95 percent, to close at 2,997.25 points from that of Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
