trillion Turkish Liras (about 212 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index went down 328.41 points, or 8.34 percent,
to close at 3,648.77 points. The industrial index dived 225.88
points, or 8.19 percent, to close at 2,574.48 points and the
service index tumbled 236.01 points, or 5.80 percent, to close at
3,873.59 points.  
</P>
