Earlier on Wednesday, Oleg Morozovm leader of the Russian
Regions group and the Duma's coordinator in the commission said
that this document is based on a political consensus of all
parliamentary factions and groups and is permeated by the idea of
mutual consultations among all branches of government on various
issues.  
