<HEADLINE> Myanmar, India Agree on Agricultural Cooperation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, August 27 (Xinhua) -- Myanmar and India agreed on some
programs of agricultural cooperation to be conducted in the next
two fiscal years during a visit to India by Myanmar Minister of
Agriculture and Irrigation Major-General Nyunt Tin.
